<template>
    <el-container>
        <el-main>

                <el-form-item label="账号：">

                        <el-input type="text" v-model="account"></el-input>
                    </el-col>
                </el-form-item>
                <el-form-item label="密码：">
                    <el-col :span="4">
                        <el-input type="password"></el-input>
                    </el-col>
                </el-form-item>
            </el-form>

        </el-main>
    </el-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: "Login",
    data() {
        return {
            account:''
        }
    },
}

</script>
